{"number":4,"verseCount":23,"verses":[[1,["Therefore, my brethren dearly beloved and longed for, my joy and crown, so ",["stand fast",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Cor. 10:12","nt/1-cor/10.12"],"; ",["16:13 (13–14)","nt/1-cor/16.13"],"; ",["Gal. 5:1","nt/gal/5.1"],"; ",["Philip. 1:27","nt/philip/1.27"],"; ",["D&C 87:8","dc-testament/dc/87.8"],"."]]]," in the Lord, ",["my",["clarity-word"]]," dearly beloved."]],[2,["I beseech Euodias, and beseech Syntyche, that they be of the same mind in the Lord."]],[3,["And I entreat thee also, true ",["yokefellow",["study-note-ref","a",["GR associate."]]],", help those women which laboured with me in the gospel, with Clement also, and ",["with",["clarity-word"]]," other my fellowlabourers, whose names ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," in the ",["book of life",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Book of Life","tg/book-of-life"],"."]]],"."]],[4,["Rejoice in the Lord alway: ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," again I say, Rejoice."]],[5,["Let your ",["moderation",["study-note-ref","a",["GR gentleness. ",["TG Modesty","tg/modesty"],"; ",["Temperance","tg/temperance"],"."]]]," be known unto all men. The Lord ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," at hand."]],[6,[["Be",["study-note-ref","a",["GR Don’t be unduly concerned about anything."]]]," ",["careful",["study-note-ref","b",["JST Philip. 4:6 … afflicted … ",["Ps. 55:22","ot/ps/55.22"],"; ",["Prov. 16:3","ot/prov/16.3"],"; ",["Matt. 6:25","nt/matt/6.25"],"."]]]," for nothing; but in every thing by ",["prayer",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Prayer","tg/prayer"],"."]]]," and supplication with ",["thanksgiving",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Thanksgiving","tg/thanksgiving"],"."]]]," let your requests be made known unto God."]],[7,["And the ",["peace",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Peace of God","tg/peace-of-god"],"."]]]," of God, which passeth all ",["understanding",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Understanding","tg/understanding"],"."]]],", shall ",["keep",["study-note-ref","c",["GR guard."]]]," your hearts and minds through Christ Jesus."]],[8,["Finally, brethren, whatsoever things are ",["true",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Truth","tg/truth"],"."]]],", whatsoever things ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," ",["honest",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Honesty","tg/honesty"],"."]]],", whatsoever things ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," ",["just",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Righteousness","tg/righteousness"],"."]]],", whatsoever things ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," ",["pure",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Purity","tg/purity"],"."]]],", whatsoever things ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," ",["lovely",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Beauty","tg/beauty"],"."]]],", ",["whatsoever",["study-note-ref","f",[["A of F 1:13","pgp/a-of-f/1.13"],"."]]]," things ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," of good report; if ",["there be",["clarity-word"]]," any ",["virtue",["study-note-ref","g",[["TG Chastity","tg/chastity"],"; ",["Virtue","tg/virtue"],"."]]],", and if ",["there be",["clarity-word"]]," any praise, ",["think",["study-note-ref","h",[["TG Motivations","tg/motivations"],"; ",["Study","tg/study"],"."]]]," on these things."]],[9,["Those things, which ye have both learned, and ",["received",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Thes. 4:1","nt/1-thes/4.1"],"."]]],", and heard, and seen in me, do: and the God of peace shall be with you."]],[10,["But I rejoiced in the Lord greatly, that now at the last your ",["care",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Cor. 11:9","nt/2-cor/11.9"],"."]]]," of me hath flourished again; wherein ye were also careful, but ye ",["lacked",["study-note-ref","b",[["Philip. 2:30 (25, 30)","nt/philip/2.30"],"."]]]," opportunity."]],[11,["Not that I speak in respect of want: for I have learned, in whatsoever state I am, ",["therewith",["clarity-word"]]," to be ",["content",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Contentment","tg/contentment"],"."]]],"."]],[12,["I know both how to be ",["abased",["study-note-ref","a",["GR humble. ",["TG Self-Sacrifice","tg/self-sacrifice"],"."]]],", and I know how to abound: every where and in all things I am instructed both to be full and to be hungry, both to abound and to suffer need."]],[13,["I can do all things through ",["Christ",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 15:5 (4–5)","nt/john/15.5"],"."]]]," which ",["strengtheneth",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Tim. 1:12","nt/1-tim/1.12"],"; ",["Alma 26:12 (11–13)","bofm/alma/26.12"],"."]]]," me."]],[14,["Notwithstanding ye have well done, that ye did ",["communicate",["study-note-ref","a",["GR participate."]]]," with my affliction."]],[15,["Now ye Philippians know also, that in the beginning of the gospel, when I departed from Macedonia, no church communicated with me as concerning giving and receiving, but ye only."]],[16,["For even in Thessalonica ye sent once and again unto my necessity."]],[17,["Not because I desire a gift: but I desire ",["fruit",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rom. 15:28 (25–28)","nt/rom/15.28"],"; ",["Titus 3:14","nt/titus/3.14"],"."]]]," that may abound to your account."]],[18,["But I have all, and ",["abound",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Cor. 9:8","nt/2-cor/9.8"],"."]]],": I am full, having received of ",["Epaphroditus",["study-note-ref","b",[["Philip. 2:25 (25–30)","nt/philip/2.25"],"."]]]," the things ",["which were sent",["clarity-word"]]," from you, an odour of a sweet smell, a sacrifice acceptable, wellpleasing to God."]],[19,["But my God shall supply all your ",["need",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 23:1","ot/ps/23.1"],"."]]]," according to his ",["riches",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Treasure","tg/treasure"],"."]]]," in glory by Christ Jesus."]],[20,["Now unto God and our Father ",["be",["clarity-word"]]," glory for ever and ever. Amen."]],[21,["Salute every saint in Christ Jesus. The brethren which are with me greet you."]],[22,["All the saints salute you, chiefly they that are of ",["Cæsar’s",["study-note-ref","a",[["Philip. 1:13","nt/philip/1.13"],"."]]]," household."]],[23,["The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ ",["be",["clarity-word"]]," with you all. Amen."]]],"volume":"nt"}